\c 17
\s Ilizwe elanikwa isizwe sakoManase
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusiba lenkatho yesizwe sakoManase, ngoba wayelizibulo likaJosefa\x + Gen. 41.51; 46.20; 48.18.\x*, \add enge\add*kaMakiri izibulo likaManase uyise kaGileyadi\x + Gen. 50.23. Nani 26.29; 32.39,40. Josh. 13.31. 1 Lan. 7.14.\x*; ngoba yena wayengumuntu wempi; ngakho waba leGileyadi leBashani\x + Dute. 3.13.\x*.
\v 2 Yayikhona njalo eyabaseleyo babantwana bakoManase ngokwensendo zabo\x + Nani 26.29-32.\x*, eyabantwana bakoAbiyezeri, leyabantwana bakoHeleki, leyabantwana bakoAsiriyeli, leyabantwana bakoShekema\x + Hlu. 6.11,24; 8.2,32. 1 Lan. 7.18.\x*, leyabantwana bakoHeferi\x + Nani 26.29-32.\x*, leyabantwana bakoShemida\x + Nani 26.29-32.\x*. Laba ngabantwana besilisa bakaManase indodana kaJosefa ngokwensendo zabo.
\p
\v 3 Kodwa uZelofehadi indodana kaHeferi indodana kaGileyadi indodana kaMakiri indodana kaManase wayengelamadodana, kodwa amadodakazi. Lala ngamabizo amadodakazi akhe: OMahla loNowa, uHogila, uMilka loTiriza\x + Nani 26.33; 27.1; 36.2,11. 1 Lan. 7.15.\x*.
\v 4 Asesondela phambi kukaEleyazare umpristi laphambi kukaJoshuwa indodana kaNuni\x + 14.1.\x* laphambi kweziphathamandla, esithi: IN\nd kosi\nd* yalaya uMozisi ukusinika ilifa phakathi kwabafowethu\x + Nani 27.6,7.\x*. Ngakho wawanika ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* ilifa phakathi kwabafowabo bakayise.
\v 5 Ngakho kwawela inkatho ezilitshumi kuManase\x + 17.2,3.\x*, ngaphandle kwelizwe leGileyadi leBashani, elingaphetsheya kweJordani\x + 13.29-31.\x*.
\v 6 Ngoba amadodakazi kaManase adla ilifa phakathi kwamadodana akhe. Lelizwe leGileyadi laba ngelabaseleyo bamadodana akoManase.
\p
\v 7 Umngcele wakoManase wasusukela eAsheri usiya eMikimethathi\x + 16.6.\x* ephambi kweShekema\x + Gen. 12.6; 33.18; 35.4; 37.12-14. Josh. 20.7; 21.21; 24.1,25,32. Hlu. 8.31; 9.1; 1 Kho. 12.1,25. 1 Lan. 6.67. 2 Lan. 10.1. Hlab. 60.6. Jer. 41.5. Seb. 7.16.\x*; lomngcele waya ngakwesokunene kubahlali beEni-Tapuwa\x + 15.34.\x*.
\v 8 UManase waba lelizwe leTapuwa\x + 15.34.\x*, kodwa iTapuwa emngceleni kaManase yayingeyabantwana bakoEfrayimi.
\v 9 Lomngcele wehlela esifuleni iKana eningizimu kwesifula. Imizi le ngeyakoEfrayimi phakathi kwemizi yakoManase\x + 16.9.\x*. Lomngcele wakoManase usenyakatho kwesifula, lokuphuma kwawo kuselwandle.
\v 10 Eningizimu lalingelakoEfrayimi, lenyakatho lalingelakoManase, lolwandle lungumngcele wakhe. LeAsheri bahlangana enyakatho, leIsakari empumalanga.
\v 11 Ngoba koIsakari loAsheri uManase\x + 1 Lan. 7.29.\x* wayeleBeti-Sheyani lemizana yayo\x + 17.16. Hlu. 1.27. 1 Kho. 4.12. 1 Sam. 31.10,12; 2 Sam. 21.12.\x*, leIbileyamu lemizana yayo\x + Hlu. 1.27. 2 Kho. 9.27. 1 Lan. 6.70; Josh. 21.25.\x*, labahlali beDori lemizana yayo, labahlali beEni-Dori lemizana yayo\x + 1 Sam. 28.7. Hlab. 83.10.\x*, labahlali beThahanakhi lemizana yayo\x + Hlu. 5.19.\x*, labahlali beMegido lemizana yayo\x + Hlu. 5.19.\x*: Amadundulu amathathu.
\v 12 Kodwa abantwana bakoManase babengelakho ukuxotsha elifeni leyomizi\x + Hlu. 1.27,28.\x*, kodwa amaKhanani ayefuna ukuhlala kulelolizwe.
\v 13 Kodwa kwathi lapho abantwana bakoIsrayeli sebelamandla bawasebenzisa amaKhanani njengezibhalwa, kodwa kabawaxotshanga lokuwaxotsha elifeni\x + 16.10.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Abantwana bakoJosefa\x + 16.4.\x* basebekhuluma kuJoshuwa\x + Nani 13.8.\x* besithi: Unginikeleni inkatho eyodwa lesabelo esisodwa ukuba yilifa\x + Gen. 48.5,22.\x*, kube kanti ngiyisizwe esikhulu, njengoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ingibusisile kuze kube lapha\x + Gen. 48.19. Nani 26.34,37.\x*?
\v 15 UJoshuwa wasesithi kubo: Uba uyisizwe esikhulu, wena yenyukela eguswini\x + 2 Sam. 18.6,17.\x*, uzicentele khona elizweni lamaPerizi leleziqhwaga\x + 17.18. Hez. 23.47.\x*, nxa intaba yakoEfrayimi iminyene kuwe\x + 24.33.\x*.
\v 16 Abantwana bakoJosefa basebesithi: Intaba kayisanelanga, njalo kulenqola zensimbi\x + 11.6.\x* lamaKhanani wonke ahlala elizweni lesihotsha, lawaseBeti-Sheyani lemizana yayo, lawasesigodini seJizereyeli\x + Hlu. 6.33. Hos. 1.5. Josh. 19.18. 1 Kho. 4.12; 18.45,46; 21.1,23; 2 Kho. 8.29; 9.10,15. 10.6,7. 2 Lan. 22.6. Josh. 15.56.\x*.
\v 17 UJoshuwa wasekhuluma kundlu kaJosefa, kuEfrayimi lakuManase esithi: Uyisizwe esikhulu, futhi ulamandla amakhulu; kawuyikuba lenkatho eyodwa,
\v 18 kodwa intaba izakuba ngeyakho; ngoba iligusu, uzalicenta, lokuphuma kwalo kube ngokwakho, ngoba uzawaxotsha elifeni amaKhanani, lanxa elenqola zensimbi, lanxa elamandla\x + 11.6.\x*\x + Dute. 20.1.\x*.